column5: I just saw a video of a scuba diver trying to "ride" a shark. It ends about as well as you'd expect.     Some never grow out of it.
Should have put life jackets on them right away
Is it against the law to ride around on a chunk of Ice, but what is the required safety equipment for a vessel over 18'? I didn't see a whistle anywhere.
What ever happened to natural selection? Are you sure we want these boys to grow up and have kids??
